headline: GE and 5 More Stocks That Can Win as AI Shakes Up the Economy
summary: Manufacturing and aerospace & defense stocks are turning out to be potential havens as artificial intelligence disrupts industries from software to financial technology and professional services.  “AI will enable a structural reduction in the cost of doing business for many commercial aerospace companies, supporting higher through-cycle margins,” wrote Deutsche Bank analyst Scott Deuschle in a Monday note.

headline: Wall Street Analysts Think Eaton (ETN) Is a Good Investment: Is It?
summary: Based on the average brokerage recommendation (ABR), Eaton (ETN) should be added to one's portfolio. Wall Street analysts' overly optimistic recommendations cast doubt on the effectiveness of this highly sought-after metric. So, is the stock worth buying?

headline: Evercore ISI Group Maintains In-Line on Eaton Corp, Raises Price Target to $407
